Package: readcorona
Type: Package
Title: a simple package to read corona data using COVID-19 API (https://corona.ndo.dev/)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Paolo Veronesi
Maintainer: Paolo Veronesi <paulvern@gmail.com>
Description: Use corona_timespan(country,timespan) to get the data for a country and a "day","week","month" or "year"    Use corona_daily(country,rating,source) to get the data for a country with a rating and a specific source.      Use corona_countries(country) to get the data for a specific country.      Use corona_datasources() and corona_meta() to get all the datasources and metadata of the covid-19 API
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
